{
  "stem": "1641.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We retreated 100 miles, but only to-- in order to-- to get the Russians surrounded later.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the-- and Hitler knows what he's doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We shorten our front, which was very beneficial for Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so each time they shortened the line, this was always 200 kilometers more to the-- to the West, near-- nearer to Berlin each time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyhow, we went to the movie in the big snow, and I came to New Year's Eve party.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the SS man there at the table, laid out with French champagne and salami and Hungarian paprika, pate, and everything, and they said-- they said, eat, Jew, eat, eat, because it'll be a good year for you, Jew.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Probably you will be liberated in a few months' time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The war is finished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Germany lost.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- he was drunk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The SS man next to me, he was drinking the champagne.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was-- they were all drunk, but he was particularly drunk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said-- and he says, ah, it's all right for you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's good to be a Jew now because you'll be free soon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But what will happen to us?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who knows what they will do with us, because they don't like us very much, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, after all, we did some bad things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it wasn't our fault.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, I got nothing against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I quite like them, in fact.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They're quite funny people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I have nothing against them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But still, you know, order is order.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I did some bad things, I suppose, but-- So actually, he was building up this friendship to me so in case the-- they come in like with the-- I could say a good, few kind words for him later on, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was drunk.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
